<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>تَفْسِيرُ سُورَةِ الْكَهْف<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{فَلَعَلَّكَ بَاخِعٌ نَفْسَكَ عَلَى آثَارِهِمْ إِنْ لَمْ يُؤْمِنُوا بِهَذَا الْحَدِيثِ أَسَفًا}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص٨٧:</span> <span class="c3">{بَاخِعٌ}</span>: مُهْلِكٌ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c3">{أَسَفًا}</span>: نَدَمًا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) [الكهف: ٦]</p> </div>